    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped coriander stalks</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add the<strong> coconut stock </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened</p>",
